</table><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Nothing here is ever legal advice, but=
 if you are a regular Money Stuff reader and your friend comes to you and s=
ays =E2=80=9Chey I=E2=80=99ve got a hot illegal insider tip that a company =
is about to announce really good news, what securities should I trade to ma=
ke money from that tip,=E2=80=9D=C2=A0I=C2=A0hope that you will not reply =
=E2=80=9Cmy man, you must trade short-dated out-of-the-money call options o=
n that company.=E2=80=9D No! Bad! That=E2=80=99s not how you do it! This is=
 <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/26291849.269650/a=
HR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMTgtMDgtMTIvdGhl=
